    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. Mechanically, the engine is currently experiencing frequent overheating and a noticeable loss of power, while the transmission exhibits hard shifting and delayed engagement. The exterior shows significant wear, including several deep scratches, minor rust spots on the wheel arches, and a faded clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely require towing to its next destination.",
