    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit features a well-preserved aesthetic and a robust mechanical history, ensuring a dependable driving experience. Representing a significant value proposition within its class, this vehicle undergoes a rigorous assessment to meet our standards of functional excellence and interior refinement. A premier choice for the professional driver seeking quality and value.",
      "price": 31500.0,
